metadata.name: 0.0050 Staked JELLY/USDC SLP
metadata.description:
WARNING: Staking NFTs are a new type of Defi NFT and Opensea does not update staked position information in real time. 

##AMOUNTS (refresh Metadata to update)

 Staked JELLY/USDC SLP on last refresh was 0.0050

Unclaimed $JELLY rewards on last refresh was 124859

##Checks before trading

Staking NFTs are a new type of Defi NFT and the underlying asset value can change. For this reason, it is not recommended to put in future offers on these NFTs, safer to use buy now price. Note that the NFT owner is able to partially unstake in the Farm which will reduce the SLP staked in the NFT and they are able to claim the rewards. Before buying a Staking NFT, refresh the Metadata so you can see the latest updates on the value held. 

 ##Staking NFT 
This NFT represents Staked JELLY/USDC SLP in the Sweet Pool. When it is bought or sold, the value of the staked position is transferred to the new owner. 

##Sweet Pool 
The Sweet Pool is where $JELLY farming rewards are earnt.  

##NFT holders 
This NFT can be traded freely on the secondary market like any other NFT, you can also transfer this NFT to a vault to keep your staked LPs safe. The NFT was minted at the time LP tokens were staked. Any wallet holding this NFT gets access to Claim the rewards and Unstake the LP tokens. A wallet can hold multiple NFTs from the same pool and these display on the Jelly protocol UI as a cumulative staked balance of LPs. 

##Jelly Farming 
 Claim, Stake and Unstake from the Jelly Pools using Jelly Protocol at [https://app.jelly.io/farms/0xF897C014a57298DA3453f474312079cC6cB140c0](https://app.jelly.io/farms/0xF897C014a57298DA3453f474312079cC6cB140c0)
